New Invocable Actions

Get to know the invocable actions available with Digital lending for Financial Services Cloud.

Check in a contract document version: Use the new checkInContractDocumentVersion action.
Create a contract for a specified record: Use the new createClmContract action.
Perform actions on a contract based on its status: Use the new performContractAction action.
Send a contract to specified recipients for e-signature: Use the new sendContractForESignature action.
